channel.title: A fatal java error
channel.description:
Hello,
I saw somebody who had this and wondered what it exactly meant.
A fatal error has been detected by the Java Runtime Environment: # # EXCEPTION_ACCESS_VIOLATION (0xc0000005) at pc=0x06fa7c99, pid=2560, tid=2732 # # JRE version: 6.0_18-b07 # Java VM: Java HotSpot(TM) Client VM (16.0-b13 mixed mode, sharing windows-x86 )
# Problematic frame: # C [ig4icd32.dll+0x117c99]
Thanks
Pk george1
